title: Mind Movies From IgetRealTv, Real To Reel Media, Scott Ercoliani
description:
The Health DVD

 
The health DVD runs 58 minutes and contains 10 inspiring videos filled with the theme of healthy living; including the alignment of Body, Mind, and Spirit. It is a powerful reminder that our well-being begins with SELF.
The Gratitude DVD

 
The gratitude DVD runs 55 minutes and contains 10 videos designed to enrich and empower our experience of being alive. It is produced using cutting-edge audio/video editing techniques, developed to inspire fresh thoughts, unique perspectives, new pathways and unlimited possibilities. It reminds us that we are all connected and invites us to open our hearts and get present to the miracle of life
The Freedom DVD

 
The freedom DVD runs 60 minutes and contains 10 powerful videos that provide a clearing for freedom and peace of mind. Begin to form new synaptic connections. Cause a new view of life for yourself.
